name: Silents of the Liquid Palette
description: Hailing from the high reaches of Mt. Kalfus, the Silents of the Liquid Palette are known for their primarily liquid-based diet. Where do they get their protein? Now renowned portrayers - those who are able to summon their imaginings into reality via brushstroke, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
